reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great desk for the price
reviews.reviewText: This was very easy to assemble and is the perfect desk for my home office-everything has a place and I love all of the drawers (they are fabric, btw). It is much easier for me to keep things organized and uncluttered.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars You get what you pay for
reviews.reviewText: Took me and the wife give or take a hour to assemble, everything was labeled correctly and the instructions were clear and easy to follow but the allen keys that are supplied are a bit on the smaller side so it made it difficult for me with larger hands to hold on and turn the key. The desk is holding all the weight i have on it pretty well, wobbles a little too much for my liking when i nudge it from rolling back from the desk or accidently nudge it when i turn in my chair. But overall you get what you pay for, its what you'd expect or maybe just a bit better (emphasis on bit) for the price that it is currently listed at (149.99).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: just perfect for what we need

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a huge upgrade from my old computer desk, and i love it! Set up is pretty simple and straightforwardLove the top shell finally i can put all my mini pc somewhere that does not take up my entire computer space. Overall clean and well worth it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
